Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:22.67,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清風　雲彩　仰望群星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:30.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸中的悸動　如波濤洶湧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:38.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無窮　無盡　戰火連綿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:46.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等揚帆　即日踏上征途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:53.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕有暗閻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:01:01.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻塞前行之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:13.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙想　祈福　唯願君平安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:28.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0}向無盡宇宙{\fsp-9}、{\fsp1.5}出征
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:08.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無重力的暗閻　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:10.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:19.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比烏斯環一般　命運九轉輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:28.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:34.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回轉{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}陰陽相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:39.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之骰一經擲出　就已無法停止轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:42.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:50.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅之風揚　我只欲逆風直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:53.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你緊緊擁入懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:24:01.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之劍{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}斬斷這一昏暗的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:08.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨彷徨　{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Lost In Space
