Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1298,885)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}席拉克沙星域會戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬的對象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的泰坦尼亞不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他主動請纓前去交涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻無果而終
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}哲力胥·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我親率大軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把謀反之人一一處決了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此言尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你都像褚士朗卿那樣心存幻想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1347,923)\fad(500,500)}伊德里斯·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1347,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イドリス・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下認為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應當再次對提蘭基亞進行勸降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}無地藩王 亞術曼·泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}無地藩王 アジュマーン・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸降嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 勸降太便宜他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忤逆泰坦尼亞之人 向來都要誅殺殆盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿有自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在受降之際 要對方一併獻上主犯的首級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(759,923)\fad(500,500)}亞歷亞伯特·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(759,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アリアバート・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說提蘭基亞的大公妃已經過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不過是個政治傀儡罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不也如此說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將幕後的重臣們以叛逆罪處死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公一脈就此斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提蘭基亞歸於泰坦尼亞麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 對方不可能答應這種條件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只有一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武裝起義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該會想招攬更多同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日燈火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對泰坦尼亞心存不滿的蟲豸們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會為光亮所引 聚集到一處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周邊諸國有些尚未表態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好藉機判明他們對泰坦尼亞的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對亂黨斬草除根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星提蘭基亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星テュランジア
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}提蘭基亞軍 康諾特少將
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}テュランジア軍 コンノート少将
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢愚弄我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}維爾達納帝國軍 沙朗·亞姆傑卡爾提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国軍 サラーム・アムゼカール提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為你們做事欠考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不投降 泰坦尼亞必會派兵前來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵來將擋 水來土掩！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我軍能動員的艦艇只有三千餘艘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要我接受這種條件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我都會被處死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就甘心領死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能一戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰死沙場 或是坐以待斃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不是全無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能拉攏到周邊諸國和反泰坦尼亞聯合軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}提蘭基亞軍 哈斐茲少將
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}テュランジア軍 ハーフェズ少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合各國兵力 艦艇數量可以輕鬆過萬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上派使者前去遊說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方肯定會樂於協助的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可難說 最好不要太指望外人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們提蘭基亞一亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就輪到他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會不知道這個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}戰艦晨曦女神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}戦艦アウストラ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿似乎喜歡擴大戰事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若把周邊諸國捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會演變為久違的大會戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也能藉機謀取私利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒有發言權
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的任務剛剛失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我們同病相憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你的禁閉被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的指揮多半是哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有我出場的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1091,923)\fad(500,500)}褚士朗·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1091,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ジュスラン・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下的舉動自有深意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想必很快就能挽回名譽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願借褚士朗卿的金口玉言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望諸國能作出理智的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞永遠是值得敬畏的對象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾賓格王國 王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国 王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可 公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下正在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是給他看看這盆怪草罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父皇總是推說他很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾任性一下也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話說得太孩子氣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾賓格王國 第二公主莉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国 第二王女リディア
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然出爾反爾 太卑劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會遺臭萬年的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是提蘭基亞公國的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他提議聯手反抗泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然派那種無禮狂徒當使者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個國家的前途可想而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚會栽在泰坦尼亞手上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星盧塔西 艾斯特拉德府
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星リュテッヒ エストラード邸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天賜良機啊 艾斯特拉德閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於那些人的叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞的統治根基有所鬆動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事的伊德里斯現在也去了天城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼 他們都無從應對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該站出來了 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(821,923)\fad(500,500)}艾斯特拉德·泰坦尼亞侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(821,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エストラード・タイタニア侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位難道忘了我也是泰坦尼亞的一員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}維爾達納帝國司法大臣 赫拉瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国司法大臣 ヘラウァー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下官看來 只有閣下才配做泰坦尼亞的藩王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前 憑什麼不是閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(806,848)\fad(500,500)}維爾達納帝國民政大臣 努尼艾司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(806,918)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国民政大臣 ヌニエス
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是身為弟弟的亞術曼被選為藩王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1283,923)\fad(500,500)}維爾達納帝國內務大臣 薩格登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1283,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国内務大臣 ザグデン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下就沒有起疑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許多言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下認為自己贏不了亞術曼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有選我 而是選上了亞術曼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為自己在實力上遜於對方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 才會被弟弟奪去藩王之位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但亞術曼一死 下任藩王就是他的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起四公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是哥哥更為世人所認同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們就從背後掌權
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 帝國就高枕無憂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不接受提議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(722,923)\fad(500,500)}法爾密·泰坦尼亞子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(722,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}バルアミー・タイタニア子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用掩飾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是他們所提議的政變一事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在暗中聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算發動政變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也贏不了泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的敵手不是叔父亞術曼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還要說自己沒有勝算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前 我滿心歡喜地認為父親必能當上藩王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 您難道甘願就此終老一生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我老了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至今日 我心中的藩王也只有父親一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你憑什麼認為我會覬覦藩王之位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也是泰坦尼亞一脈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有野心很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但前路絕非坦途
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要發動政變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實很像那些小人物的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們卻不知道同夥中有我們的眼線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯緊艾斯特拉德確實沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時此刻 比起諸君他離藩王之位更近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個近衛軍司令可謂不辱使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說要如何處置艾斯特拉德閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此話怎講？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和你對提蘭基亞的政策如出一轍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請軍務大臣當那盞聚蟲的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要盯緊他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動導航裝置 啟動完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨曦女神自動牽引至指定船塢停靠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣未能完成使命 愧對殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能糾結於過去 而要放眼未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對提蘭基亞的策略 卿已經有所耳聞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 伊德里斯卿才氣橫溢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣衷心佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕計劃有變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞如今威嚴尚在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一同做起了壁上觀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一國也沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾賓格等國起初回應了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在關鍵時刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞就如此恐怖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法得到各國的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局勢對我們很不利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 早已沒有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集全部兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞也不是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱貝羅斯會戰不是有例在先嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是凱貝羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連那種舊船都要用上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是背水一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要動員一切力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是士官學校的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也接到了出擊命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界末日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我想請問下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二艦隊在哪裡集合？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 怎麼對亞姆傑卡爾提督說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1121,923)\fad(500,500)}懷茲中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1121,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ワイズ中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷茲中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是准將
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實在過不慣軍旅生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就退役當了商人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半數是走私業務…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為軍人居然搞走私？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛國心使然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一被泰坦尼亞掌了權
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走私是要掉腦袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是全家處死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐的隸屬是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二艦隊的分艦隊指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率領五艘驅逐艦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待你的表現 中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二艦隊司令部是右邊的建築
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必讓臣前去征討
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身為近衛軍司令 脫不開身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗卿剛逃回來 需要休整
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣認為可以交給哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷亞伯特卿意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望殿下開恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 孤就命你前往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若再失敗的話 你的爵位恐怕不保
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我見識一下您的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魏格特炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是方修利用在你身上的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何推薦此計？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 這一戰術十分有效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其次 透過肯定方修利的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷亞伯特卿的氣量也會受到肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後就不會有人再用那種戰術了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱貝羅斯會戰會成為純粹的偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙策啊 褚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你應該清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此役只許勝 不許敗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不準備採納這一計策嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就聽取您的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能怪我實力不濟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}亞歷亞伯特艦隊旗艦 金羊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アリアバート艦隊旗艦 ゴールデン・シープ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}提蘭基亞軍 軍港
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}テュランジア軍 軍港
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是懷茲中佐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 下官負責指揮第81小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出擊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官盡力而為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方居然只有三千餘艘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也深感意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運的是 我們能和敵人對等作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方大將是亞歷亞伯特公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他是來一雪凱貝羅斯之恥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官正是為此想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方應該不想一再失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但敵艦數量卻不多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕對方有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為職業習慣 下官有些多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷亞伯特公爵是正統的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會耍什麼詭計的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定是在小看我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提蘭基亞軍在席拉克沙星域佈陣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這道防線一旦被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}席拉克沙星域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}シラクサ星域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本國之前將再無屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可謂背水一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10時方向出現大量艦影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方佈下了半月陣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此陣比起進攻 更注重防守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷亞伯特那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被凱貝羅斯一戰嚇破了膽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦進入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快重整陣型 一舉轉守為攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷亞伯特卿有些不堪重負嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火 給我狠狠地打！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍佔優
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是他們的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會敗在士官學校的菜鳥手上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞也不過如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趁熱打鐵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 全艦突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方艦隊衝過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們上鉤了 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方主力 急速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調魏格特炮出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投在屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魏格特炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魏格特炮 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅一擊 就讓我軍損失了半數艦艇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魏格特炮 凱貝羅斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是泰坦尼亞的恐怖之處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是魏格特炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分艦隊指揮官來電
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官閣下 請下令攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷茲中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊？你說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人因為魏格特炮的自爆而陣型大亂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若趁機突擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能一舉擊沉泰坦尼亞的旗艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入敵方腹地的話 只會全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算全軍覆沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要幹掉了敵方大將亞歷亞伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我軍的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區中佐竟敢插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直無法無天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 攻擊太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是一時撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下 敵方撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點重整陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11時方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俯角40度發現敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有六艘驅逐艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝金羊直衝過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方也有勇者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 準備炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧 亞歷亞伯特！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷茲中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這種軍人是敵不過泰坦尼亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有人能贏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人肯定無法以常理猜度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}「正直老人」號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}「正直じいさん」号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1248,870)\fad(500,500)}方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1248,940)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ファン・ヒューリック
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得細細品味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}米蘭達·卡西米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミランダ・カジミール
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經快斷糧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去補給不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但泰坦尼亞在前方打仗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見沒 已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}亞朗·麥佛迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アラン・マフディー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就不問問哪邊贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想乾啃麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又死了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但褚士朗大人已經盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.15,0:22:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提蘭基亞公國從宇宙地圖上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.87,0:24:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想去補充燃料 沒想到那個星球上滿是宇宙海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星旗軍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那個男人也在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.97,0:24:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.25,0:24:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李博士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(599,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}流星旗下


